text:
Self-Evaluation Questionnaire


Please take a moment to think how you felt after repeating the previous word.

To respond, please rate each statement below by clicking on a number from 1 to 7, whereby 1 = you strongly disagree with the statement, while 7 = you strongly agree with the statement. There are no right or wrong answers. Do not spend too much time on any one statement.
I wondered if I had done the right thing by repeating it
I wondered if I really need to repeat it
I wondered if I should have repeat it
I wondered if I made the right choice repeating it
